# SimpleOS Services
#
# Userspace services communicating via kernel IPC:
#   - Init / service manager
#   - VFS (Virtual Filesystem)
#   - FAT32 filesystem driver
#   - Network stack (lwIP initially, pure Simple later)
#   - Logging / journal
#   - PCI manager (device enumeration and driver grant)
#   - LLM MCP server (OS control via MCP tools + widget DSL)
